    <abstract>
      <t>This memo specifies the details for establishing and maintaining a Secure Session Layer Services (SSLS) association between two applications using the Host Identity Protocol (HIP [RFC7401]). This is primarily achieved by adding SSLS specific HIP parameters for the HIP base exchange. The SSLS association state and security boundaries are also defined.</t>
